  "detailed_description": "<strong>Game Introduction</strong><br><br>The protagonist transfers to a new school and decides to join a band club, beginning their club life alongside fellow members. However, instead of the exciting club life they imagined, they face a series of unexpected events...<br><br>What kind of adventures await you?<br><br><br><br><strong>Synopsis</strong><br><br>How was your school life?<br><br>Being a transfer student who doesn't know how to approach others, the only friend I have in the entire school is a quirky otaku. Amidst a lonely school life, I was suddenly asked by a beautiful female student to join her club. Although the invitation was unexpectedly abrupt, upon joining the club, I soon realize there are no fairy-tale princesses in real life.<br><br><br><br><strong>Character Introduction</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991980/extras/326e3b1f56b5be9cf5cf11700cc0514f.avif?t=1719824287\" width=600 height=416 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991980/extras/c7009b2e5e72a9664ade141b32b6427d.avif?t=1719824287\" width=600 height=416 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991980/extras/a972e5bcc2e7aec0fe33a877e5e76110.avif?t=1719824287\" width=600 height=416 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991980/extras/15932ba43f5db0039479cbff01883cef.avif?t=1719824287\" width=600 height=416 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991980/extras/2f005444b6b852e5401e02223253fbce.avif?t=1719824287\" width=600 height=416 /></span><br><br><br><strong>Game Features</strong><br><br>Over 15 hours of immersive gameplay<br><br>More than 80 different character expressions<br><br>CG illustrations crafted specifically for special moments<br><br>Background illustrations that feel like you're stepping into the screen",
